description.en: The Manhua is loosely inspired by Soulcalibur 1 but changes the setting to a fictional SciFi one as opposed to one based on actual history. The biggest change is the story is focused around Hwang with Kilik acting as a supporting character.
description.ru: Маньхуа пересказывал события первой части, но с Хваном в главной роли и в сеттинге с элементами научной фантастики.

description.en: Two stories about the use of first names between Oikawa and Kageyama.

A collection of oneshots.  
  
1. Yozora ni Kiss (夜空にKISS, Night Sky Kiss) by Miyasaka Kaho  
Hitomi is about to change schools, and before she does, she wants to go out with a bang at the cultural festival. Will committee chair Matsunaga-kun help?  
  
2. Powder Snow ni KISS (粉雪にKISS) by Miyasaka Kaho  
Continuation of the first story.  
  
3. Shinai (深愛) by Nakamura Sayumi  
  
4. Dakara, zutto… (だから、ずっと・・・) by Haga Yuina  
  
5. Koi to Iu Shiromono (恋というシロモノ) by Fukami Sakana  
  
6. Dream by Ibuki Kaede  
  
7. Dakkai Letter Sakusou Love (奪回Letter 錯綜Love) by Minami Kanan  
  
8. Wild Cinderella (ワイルド・シンデレラ) by Satsuki Mikiko

Nagisa's biology teacher, Mr. Fujiki, always warned her to watch out for guys who would take advantage of her. But it's the last day of summer break, and Nagisa is determined to find love before she goes back to school! The handsome man she meets gives Nagisa the same warning Mr. Fujiki did… but there's something important that neither of them has mentioned to her!
